/*READ ME:
REPLACE "INTERNAL_TRAINING_CANDIDATE_1" with <your database name>
REPLACE "db_source" with <your schema>
*/

CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW "${job_database_name}"."${job_source_schema_name}"."vew_flights_2016"
AS
select "flight_date", 
  "departure_time", 
  "crs_departure_time", 
  "arrival_time", 
  "crs_arrival_time", 
  "carrier", 
  "flight_number", 
  "actual_elapsed_time", 
  "airtime", 
  "origin", 
  "destination", 
  "distance_type", 
  "distance", 
  "taxi_in"
from "${job_database_name}"."${job_source_schema_name}"."training_flights"
where date_part(year, to_date("flight_date")) = 2016;
